node_7.subject: Maria Lopez
node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 9:00 am, go to Oak Hill College for classes from 10:00 am to 2:00 pm, have lunch at 2:30 pm, study at Hobbs Cafe from 3:00 pm to 5:30 pm, go home and relax for a bit, start Twitch streaming or gaming at 8:00 pm and continue until 11:00 pm, have dinner at 11:30 pm.
